Tadalafil therapy for pulmonary arterial hypertension.

Galiè N(1), Brundage BH, Ghofrani HA, Oudiz RJ, Simonneau G, Safdar Z, Shapiro 
S, White RJ, Chan M, Beardsworth A, Frumkin L, Barst RJ; Pulmonary Arterial 
